Text:
Thank you very much for this one! Now my wife will be happy (And maybe less upset that I sit at the comp. A LOT... :)) But yes, even I have to admit that she has some good songs. Even if I wouldn't like to be caught listening to them... :) 
This is the best Cher-compilation I have seen and it seems to be in rather high bitrate, so I am very grateful! Thanks again. 

Btw: I thought this torrent was dead but now it has come to life again. Very nice! 
But there are rather many egoistic downloaders here at TPB. Torrents die easily, don't they...
